</span> : <span class=\"fn\">State</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">na</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Basic.html#Cslib.LTS.MTr\">MTr</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Data/OmegaSequence/Defs.html#Cslib.ωSequence.take\">ωSequence.take</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span> <span class=\"fn\">xs</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">t</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">na</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/Automata/NA/Basic.html#Cslib.Automata.NA.start\">start</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ss</span> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inl\">Sum.inl</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ss</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Sum.inl\">Sum.inl</a> <span class=\"fn\">t</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"In an infinite execution of `NA.totalize`, as long as the NA stays in a non-sink state,\nthe execution so far corresponds to a finite execution of the original NA. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/Automata/NA/Total.html#Cslib.Automata.NA.totalize_run_mtr","kind":"theorem","line":30,"name":"Cslib.Automata.NA.totalize_run_mtr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/7f88669e78c0fa9d9c4f41a397072114cbb9aa7e/Cslib/Computability/Automata/NA/Total.lean#L30-L41"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/Automata/NA/Total.html#Cslib.Automata.NA.totalize\"><span class=\"name\">Csl